You’re tabbing wrong in the items that show the errors.
It should look like
item = 6(TAB)Cannon_base(TAB)The_cannon_is_built_on_this.(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0(TAB)0
Replace (TAB) with a real tab.
